                <head>434. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Policy toward Iraq was included in the new approach to certain Middle Eastern
                    policies, approved by President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName> on March 28, 1956. See <ref target="#d106">Document
                        106</ref>. For additional information, see <ref
                        target="frus1955-57v15#pg_409">volume XV, pages 409</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
